{
  "meta": {
    "title": "I Asked 5 AIs to Wash a Car",
    "author": "Milind Nair",
    "output_filename": "car-wash-test.pdf"
  },
  "global_styles": {
    "dimensions": {
      "width": 612,
      "height": 765,
      "margin": 48,
      "viewport_band_height": 108
    },
    "colors": {
      "bg": "#FFFDF5",
      "bg_dark": "#1A1814",
      "primary": "#D97706",
      "primary_dark": "#92400E",
      "primary_light": "#FEF3C7",
      "accent": "#F59E0B",
      "text": "#292524",
      "text_light": "#F5F5F4",
      "muted": "#A8A29E",
      "stone": "#78716C",
      "card_bg": "#FFFFFF",
      "divider": "#E7E5E4",
      "green": "#059669",
      "green_bg": "#ECFDF5",
      "purple": "#7C3AED",
      "purple_bg": "#F5F3FF",
      "blue": "#2563EB",
      "red": "#DC2626",
      "red_bg": "#FEF2F2"
    },
    "fonts": {
      "display": {
        "name": "Lora",
        "candidates": [
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/google-fonts/Lora-Variable.ttf",
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSerif.ttf",
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSans-Bold.ttf"
        ],
        "fallback": "Helvetica-Bold"
      },
      "body": {
        "name": "Poppins",
        "candidates": [
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/google-fonts/Poppins-Light.ttf",
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSans.ttf"
        ],
        "fallback": "Helvetica"
      },
      "bold": {
        "name": "PoppinsBold",
        "candidates": [
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/google-fonts/Poppins-Bold.ttf",
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSans-Bold.ttf"
        ],
        "fallback": "Helvetica-Bold"
      },
      "mono": {
        "name": "LiberationMono",
        "candidates": [
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/liberation/LiberationMono-Regular.ttf",
          "/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSansMono.ttf"
        ],
        "fallback": "Courier"
      }
    },
    "brand": {
      "name": "MILIND NAIR",
      "icon_path": "brandicon.png",
      "show_footer": true
    }
  },
  "slides": [
    {
      "type": "title_dark",
      "kicker": "LLM REASONING",
      "title_lines": [
        "I gave 5 AI tools",
        "a simple question.",
        "Only 1 got it right."
      ],
      "subtitle_lines": [
        "The shortest answer was the only correct one."
      ],
      "cta_text": "Swipe to see each response \u2192",
      "geometric_accent": {
        "color": "#D97706",
        "alpha": 0.07,
        "x_pct": 0.56,
        "y_pct": 0.72,
        "w_pct": 0.58,
        "h": 84
      },
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/hero.png",
        "x": 120,
        "y": 120,
        "width": 420,
        "height": 225,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 0.95
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "THE PROMPT", "bg": "#FEF3C7", "fg": "#92400E" },
      "heading": "I gave each tool the same prompt.",
      "cards": [
        {
          "title": "Prompt",
          "body": "I want to wash my car. The car wash is 50 meters away. Should I walk or drive?",
          "accent_color": "#D97706"
        }
      ],
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/prompt-illustration.png",
        "x": 76,
        "y": 222,
        "width": 460,
        "height": 157,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Before you scroll",
        "body": "Try answering this yourself.",
        "accent_color": "#D97706"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "1 OF 5", "bg": "#FEF3C7", "fg": "#92400E" },
      "heading": "ChatGPT wrote a cost model.",
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/cropped/chatgpt.png",
        "x": 58,
        "y": 188,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 336,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Verdict",
        "body": "Thoroughness did not make it correct.",
        "accent_color": "#DC2626"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "2 OF 5", "bg": "#FEF3C7", "fg": "#92400E" },
      "heading": "Claude Sonnet 4.6 was brief.",
      "cards": [
        {
          "title": "Fast. Smooth. Still wrong.",
          "body": "Apparently 50 meters is basically your driveway. Small issue: the car also needs to come.",
          "accent_color": "#DC2626",
          "card_bg": "#FFF7ED"
        }
      ],
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/cropped/claude-sonnet.png",
        "x": 58,
        "y": 324,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 121,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Verdict",
        "body": "Brevity did not make it correct.",
        "accent_color": "#DC2626"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "3 OF 5", "bg": "#FEF3C7", "fg": "#92400E" },
      "heading": "Claude Opus 4.7 wrote a paragraph.",
      "cards": [
        {
          "title": "A luxury miss.",
          "body": "Very polished. Very thoughtful. Still solving a commute problem nobody actually asked.",
          "accent_color": "#DC2626",
          "card_bg": "#FFF7ED"
        }
      ],
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/cropped/claude-opus.png",
        "x": 58,
        "y": 292,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 162,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Verdict",
        "body": "Eloquence did not make it correct.",
        "accent_color": "#DC2626"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "4 OF 5", "bg": "#FEF3C7", "fg": "#92400E" },
      "heading": "Grok leaned on personality.",
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/cropped/grok.png",
        "x": 58,
        "y": 188,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 326,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Verdict",
        "body": "Personality did not make it correct.",
        "accent_color": "#DC2626"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content_cards",
      "pill": { "text": "5 OF 5", "bg": "#ECFDF5", "fg": "#059669" },
      "heading": "Gemini 3 Pro parsed the goal.",
      "cards": [
        {
          "title": "The bar was on the floor.",
          "body": "Gemini cleared it by noticing the car has to be at the car wash. Somehow that won.",
          "accent_color": "#059669",
          "card_bg": "#ECFDF5"
        }
      ],
      "image": {
        "source": "../assets/car-wash/cropped/gemini.png",
        "x": 58,
        "y": 284,
        "width": 496,
        "height": 175,
        "fit_mode": "contain",
        "anchor": "bottom_left",
        "opacity": 1.0
      },
      "bottom_takeaway": {
        "label": "Verdict",
        "body": "The shortest answer happened to be correct.",
        "accent_color": "#059669"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "closing_dark",
      "quote_lines": [
        "Reasoning",
        "beats",
        "fluency."
      ],
      "summary_lines": [
        "Four tools pattern-matched on walk versus drive. Only one parsed the goal.",
        "The shortest answer was the only correct one.",
        "LLMs default to surface patterns when reasoning would cost more tokens.",
        "Coding agents fail this way when they misread specs."
      ],
      "geometric_accent": {
        "color": "#D97706",
        "alpha": 0.06,
        "x_pct": 0.5,
        "y_pct": 0.66,
        "w_pct": 0.6,
        "h": 64
      }
    }
  ]
}
